                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1033358378" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1033358378" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1033358378">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/62639604/">levana</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-05-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">民主并非一件人们如果刻意地去找就可以找到的财宝，而是在我们寻找它的过程中，在不懈的去寻找那些根本无法找到的东西的过程中，我们所付出的劳动将在民主的意义上取得丰硕的成果。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="935854549">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-935854549" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-935854549" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="935854549">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59575014/">鹿灵</a>
