              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                反面教材，社會主義自供狀。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>讀書筆記<a rel="nofollow" href="http://photo.weibo.com/1769257863/albums/detail/album_id/3656113034790477#!/mode/1/page/1" target="_blank">http://photo.weibo.com/1769257863/albums/detail/album_id/3656113034790477#!/mode/1/page/1</a>或
<a rel="nofollow" href="http://photo.renren.com/photo/336503828/album-953539110?uploadType=1&jisu=1&alltime=0" target="_blank">http://photo.renren.com/photo/336503828/album-953539110?uploadType=1&amp;jisu=1&amp;alltime=0</a>
